Package net.flytre.mechanix.api.inventory

Interface EasyInventory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.minecraft.util.Clearable, net.minecraft.inventory.Inventory, net.minecraft.inventory.SidedInventory
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DoubleInventory
    public interface EasyInventory
extends net.minecraft.inventory.SidedInventory
    Implemented inventory to prevent errors when creating your custom machine! Highly recommended over default inventory unless you need absolutely crazy behavior!
